item.title: Membership
item.description: The QAU Alumni Association North America launches its membership campaign and would like to invite you to become its inaugural members by filling out the following form. Eligibillity The membership is open to everyone who has an affiliation with QAU in any of the following capacities: Received a degree, diploma, or certificate from the University in a certified program of one year or more (regular member)

item.title: QAU-NA Journey
item.description: Interim Board Members (from left to right) - Sajida, Tariq, Faisel, Arshed, Umair, Saif, Farah, Khalid Some of the former senior Quadians, now based in North America, have been discussing the need to establish QAU Alumni in North America for quite some time. Since 2021 few former Quadians based in North America met multiple times in Toronto to formalize the alumni association.
